  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Welcome to Space </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Space Defender</strong> is a 2D arcade space shooter blending twin-stick action with RPG progression. Crafted by a solo French developer, this dynamic cosmic adventure is playable in English or French with <i>full controller support</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/9752058a02b01d210ea8749974a47cd5.poster.avif?t=1764437734\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/9752058a02b01d210ea8749974a47cd5.webm?t=1764437734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/9752058a02b01d210ea8749974a47cd5.mp4?t=1764437734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore and Fight Freely</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Journey through <strong>three unique galaxies</strong>, each with polished visuals and escalating challenges. Your ship evolves, but so do your foes! Take on <strong>missions</strong> at stations: wipe out enemy squadrons, defend outposts, or escort vulnerable ships.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Repel the Threat </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Battle Drones wreaking havoc across sectors. Wield a <strong>diverse arsenal</strong> – laser cannons, guided missiles, automated turrets, and more – to prevail. Pilot with precision, as every equipped item affects visuals and gameplay.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/1aae08c9a0f416404ed9fd31a89badd6.poster.avif?t=1764437734\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/1aae08c9a0f416404ed9fd31a89badd6.webm?t=1764437734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/1aae08c9a0f416404ed9fd31a89badd6.mp4?t=1764437734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Level Up Your Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Earn credits from missions to <strong>upgrade your ship</strong> or purchase stronger models, like the <i>Orion Cruiser</i> or <i>Vulture Frigate</i>. Equip over <strong>50 items</strong> (Cobra batteries, Hornet shields) and <strong>manage energy</strong> to optimize performance. Liberate each galaxy by aiding stations, building toward an epic final mission <i>(coming soon</i><strong>™</strong><i>)</i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/32aeb677b4056d5c3148d4c545797464.poster.avif?t=1764437734\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/32aeb677b4056d5c3148d4c545797464.webm?t=1764437734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/32aeb677b4056d5c3148d4c545797464.mp4?t=1764437734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Early Access: Join the Adventure</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Early Access, Space Defender offers many hours of gameplay but includes some bugs (UI, missions) and repetitive tasks we’re refining. New missions (massive battles, swarm) and a polished experience are planned for the full release. Commander, <i>your feedback will shape this universe</i> – <strong>jump in now!</strong> </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Welcome to Space </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Space Defender</strong> is a 2D arcade space shooter blending twin-stick action with RPG progression. Crafted by a solo French developer, this dynamic cosmic adventure is playable in English or French with <i>full controller support</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/9752058a02b01d210ea8749974a47cd5.poster.avif?t=1764437734\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/9752058a02b01d210ea8749974a47cd5.webm?t=1764437734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/9752058a02b01d210ea8749974a47cd5.mp4?t=1764437734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore and Fight Freely</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Journey through <strong>three unique galaxies</strong>, each with polished visuals and escalating challenges. Your ship evolves, but so do your foes! Take on <strong>missions</strong> at stations: wipe out enemy squadrons, defend outposts, or escort vulnerable ships.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Repel the Threat </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Battle Drones wreaking havoc across sectors. Wield a <strong>diverse arsenal</strong> – laser cannons, guided missiles, automated turrets, and more – to prevail. Pilot with precision, as every equipped item affects visuals and gameplay.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/1aae08c9a0f416404ed9fd31a89badd6.poster.avif?t=1764437734\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/1aae08c9a0f416404ed9fd31a89badd6.webm?t=1764437734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/1aae08c9a0f416404ed9fd31a89badd6.mp4?t=1764437734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Level Up Your Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Earn credits from missions to <strong>upgrade your ship</strong> or purchase stronger models, like the <i>Orion Cruiser</i> or <i>Vulture Frigate</i>. Equip over <strong>50 items</strong> (Cobra batteries, Hornet shields) and <strong>manage energy</strong> to optimize performance. Liberate each galaxy by aiding stations, building toward an epic final mission <i>(coming soon</i><strong>™</strong><i>)</i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/32aeb677b4056d5c3148d4c545797464.poster.avif?t=1764437734\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/32aeb677b4056d5c3148d4c545797464.webm?t=1764437734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731170/extras/32aeb677b4056d5c3148d4c545797464.mp4?t=1764437734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Early Access: Join the Adventure</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Early Access, Space Defender offers many hours of gameplay but includes some bugs (UI, missions) and repetitive tasks we’re refining. New missions (massive battles, swarm) and a polished experience are planned for the full release. Commander, <i>your feedback will shape this universe</i> – <strong>jump in now!</strong> </p>",
